                     <interp inst="t18320405-13-off84" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320405-13-off84" type="offenceSubcategory" value="housebreaking"></interp>
               feloniously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of Sarah Harriet Wallbridge, on the <rs id="t18320405-13-cd85" type="crimeDate">26th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-13-off84 t18320405-13-cd85"></join>
