                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-13-off95 t18320405-13-cd85"></join>, at St. Pancras, and stealing therein, 10 pairs of ear-rings, value 5l.; 1 gold cross, value 2l.; 3 diamond studs, value 3l.; 3 eye-glasses, value 2l.; 2 necklaces, value 10s.; 2 gold chains, value 5l.; 5 bracelets, value 1l.; 4 rings, value 1l.; 3 lockets, value 1l.; 1 silver mug, value 2l.; 21 silver forks, value 10l.; 20 silver spoons, value 10l.; 3 silver ladles, value 2l.; 2 silver fish-slices, value 3l.; 2 silver knives; value 10s, and 3 seals, value 2l., the goods of the said 
                     
