                     <interp inst="t18320405-13-person247" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live with Mr. Morrison, a pawnbroker, of York-street, Bryanstone-square. I believe the male prisoner to be the man who pawned a pair of coral ear-rings, for 4s., on the 3rd of March.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320405-13-person248">
                  John 
                  Druitt
               <interp inst="t18320405-13-person248" type="surname" value="Druitt"></interp>
