                     <interp inst="t18320405-13-person248" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . Q. Did you not tell the Magistrate you could not positively swear to me? A. I do not swear to you, but believe you to be the man; I have no doubt about him at all.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320405-13-person249">
                  WILLIAM 
                  ROHINSON
