                  </persName>
            , a pawnbroker, of Theobald's-road. Three brilliant diamond studs were pawned with me on the 22nd of February for 1l. 4s.; they were valued at three guineas - I have no recollection of the person, and do not remember seeing Druitt till he was at the office.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320405-13-person251">
                  JOHN 
                  LOVICK
