                     <interp inst="t18320405-13-person262" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . She identified him before the coat was put on.</p>
               <p>Two witnesses gave the prisoner, John Druitt, a good character, but they had not known him for the last fifteen months.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320405-13-person263">
                  ANN 
                  BACON
               <interp inst="t18320405-13-person263" type="surname" value="BACON"></interp>
