                     <interp inst="t18320405-13-person263" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live in Grove-place, directly opposite the prisoner, and have known him since last October; he was out of work all that time - I believe he was a very honest industrious man, but in a great deal of poverty; I saw him at his house about six o'clock on the morning he was taken.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320405-13-person264">
