                     <interp inst="t18320405-13-person267" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , a bricklayer and plasterer; he was close to me coming for the property when I was taken - after the property was found I considered it much more serious to be brought up on this charge than as a body-snatcher.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320405-13-person268">
                  JOHN 
                  DRUITT
               <interp inst="t18320405-13-person268" type="surname" value="DRUITT"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320405-13-person268" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320405-13-person268" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             - <rs id="t18320405-13-verdict89" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320405-13-verdict89" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs> - <rs id="t18320405-13-punish90" type="punishmentDescription">
